<dl id="n10075f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10075f">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10075f"> 75(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> makes absent present <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n10075f"> <li>FW unlocated</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">J&apos;ouvre le dictionnaire philosophique de Voltaire, au mot de Poste, et j&apos;y trouve: &ldquo;La poste est le lien de toutes les affaires, de toutes les n&eacute;gociations: <mark>les absents deviennent par elle pr&eacute;sents</mark>; elle est la consolation de la vie.&rdquo; <font color="green">[Opening Voltaire&apos;s philosophical dictionary to the word Post, I find &ldquo;The post is the link for all business and all negotiations. Those who are absent are made present by it. It is life&apos;s consolation.&rdquo;]</font> <small> Arthur de Rothschild, <a name="ARHD" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ARHD"><cite title="source">Histoire de la poste</cite></a> (1876) 8</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
